    Euler
    public class p003
extends java.lang.Object
implements Euler
    This class solves problem three in Project Euler. The prime factors of 13195 are 5, 7, 13 and 29. What is the largest prime factor of the number 600851475143? This solution uses a brute force algorithm

    Kamil Adem
